    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重要提示：</strong>《World War 3》中文与日文的本地化目前尚未完成，我们将在接下来的更新补丁中完成本地化工作，感谢您的耐心等待！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《World War 3》是一款多人在线战术类第一人称射击游戏，以现代全球冲突为背景。您可以在华沙、柏林与莫斯科等真实存在的区域中，与敌人进行紧张刺激的遭遇战，与您的队友一起火力压制敌人，包抄他们。在一应俱全的武器库中选择属于您的完美配装，部署载具、使用工具与无人机，呼叫战术打击来获得优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/bf25b5fd23711ac182e97352be45cc98.poster.avif?t=1762688477\" width=616 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/bf25b5fd23711ac182e97352be45cc98.webm?t=1762688477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/bf25b5fd23711ac182e97352be45cc98.mp4?t=1762688477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>基于团队的多人在线对战。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以在两个核心游戏模式中，与多达40名玩家一起投入战场。您可以在战术行动模式中（20对20），在快节奏的遭遇战中夺取分数，或是在经典的团队死亡竞赛模式中（10对10）中，想办法击杀最多敌人，获得胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/f260ec7ec8f056bee47017c0ff450787.poster.avif?t=1762688477\" width=616 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/f260ec7ec8f056bee47017c0ff450787.webm?t=1762688477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/f260ec7ec8f056bee47017c0ff450787.mp4?t=1762688477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全面战争。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用您所拥有的一切武器进行战斗。作为脚踏实地的步兵，您可以驾驶坦克与车辆，使用无人机侦查战场，并呼叫战术打击，最大程度地杀伤敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/f5762fabdfdbd20acb828ccd85628675.poster.avif?t=1762688477\" width=616 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/f5762fabdfdbd20acb828ccd85628675.webm?t=1762688477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/f5762fabdfdbd20acb828ccd85628675.mp4?t=1762688477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>以您的方式作战。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以从一应俱全的武器库中尽情选择属于您的载具、工具、无人机、炮兵与空中打击支援。选择属于您的完美装备，使用几百种独一无二的武器组件和与外观定制您的专属配装。您的载具车辆、战术装备与制服都可以进行定制，让您在战场上备受瞩目。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/14e9aad9f1b9c05056e7a48c2270345e.poster.avif?t=1762688477\" width=616 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/14e9aad9f1b9c05056e7a48c2270345e.webm?t=1762688477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/14e9aad9f1b9c05056e7a48c2270345e.mp4?t=1762688477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>的世界。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在令人惊艳的环境中作战，地理环境基于真实世界制作，细节水瓶令人难以置信。您可以前往华沙、柏林、莫斯科与波利亚尼的街道，或是斯摩棱斯克的郊区，甚至去更远的地方与敌人作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/c2e6874883d955459b97b7c64ae1115b.poster.avif?t=1762688477\" width=616 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/c2e6874883d955459b97b7c64ae1115b.webm?t=1762688477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674020/extras/c2e6874883d955459b97b7c64ae1115b.mp4?t=1762688477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>身临其境</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一枪都不会白打。尽情享受逼真的游戏特性，包括先进的弹道系统、全身意识、车辆物理机制，以及各式各样的定制内容。在不影响战斗的情况下，让游戏体验更加身临其境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
